Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:33.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}四目相望 时间于此刻静止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:37.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}故事在月夜开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:41.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}那上了锁的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:46.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}开锁的钥匙异常地单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:51.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}别怕 交给你自身的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:56.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}答案就在那前方 It's true
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:02:00.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}真是僵硬的舞步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:03.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}与你一同起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.52,0:02:06.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}时而绊倒 时而推挤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:12.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}呼吸交错的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:21.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}狂吹吧 暴风雨 响彻天际吧雷鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}带着溢出的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:29.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}天使奏响的未知旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:34.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}那幻想的序奏迸发出闪光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}那未知的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:41.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}将由我们开创
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,166)}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:49.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fad(16,266)}全速奔跑
