Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:05.11,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.44,0:00:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僵尸步那家伙把Mystletainn搞坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这个时候梅加洛出现该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可关系到我的学分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.20,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 是不是跑去哪玩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在全校面前穿着令人极度无语的打扮以及全裸的蛆虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然还好意思出来 你这暴露狂+小丑+蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.47,0:01:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的齿轮有时会朝你意想不到的地方旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果这就是盖亚对我的试炼 我觉得就该接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.72,0:01:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 因为我是被选中的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的屁股还是那么性感呢 亲爱的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过众多的战斗 最终损坏的魔装炼器Mystletainn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔装少女的姿态就这么烙印在人们的眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:03:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步名为「日常」的战斗现在开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:03.71,OT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs36\fad(260,0)}「呜呼、永别了我自己」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点击量逆天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.86,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态（日本品质）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学们一定会鄙视做出那种打扮的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我决定要接受这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是「被选中的人」所无法避免的荆棘之路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 相川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:04:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经成为流行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家刚刚还在讨论会不会到学校来采访呢 相川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 肯定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媒体什么的一定会蜂拥而至的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好好琢磨了一下 觉得相川同学还是挺有型的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强自己接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 妙子 那确实令人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对劲 谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织户
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.33,0:04:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织户？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川同学的腿…好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖亚 你要我如何接受此等试炼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 今天您在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能是怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周遭的人和事不停地朝我不希望的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时是这样的啦 嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很讨厌被瞩目的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也来一杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我还未成年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 明明那么好喝的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能喝的话真想来一杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scandal是Scan 抓住机会 冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:50.03,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔的冷笑话 没啥特别意思……大概
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 人生不如意十有八九
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是在说大叔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是常说流言不过350006575天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:10.79,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实真正应该是流言不过75天 就是流言不会长久的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,75天吗 嗯 可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精小姐 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉我又有活下去的动力了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！有空再来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间会解决一切…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nomobuyo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.64,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是咒语的第一句 呼ぶもの的颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nomobuyo那人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在刚好不在 能等会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决不了的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 相川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都说别叫友纪（tomonori）了要说几遍才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我友…友纪（yuki）就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 明天晚上去山里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山？山是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山吗 或许很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测天体？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去山里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.57,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算窝在山里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得哥哥只要做自己就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:35.45,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是内心脆弱的主人公相川步的脑补声音 CV:南央美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我需要一片远离人烟的清静之地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且友纪她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大自然很棒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气清新 星空绝美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透过与大自然一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我能重生为一个不被周遭所左右的新自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只跟友纪两个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 相川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是只有相川一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要穿的像样点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小细节就别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 现在就去看天满的繁星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天满→满天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胆多少钱嘿哟 海胆乌贼乌贼墨 海胆多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候才能到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈 别再发牢骚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了累死了累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你穿凉鞋过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 别小瞧山了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆回去算了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈 这种地方可没厕所哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 让人头疼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到星星了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要去的地方可是比这漂亮的多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的事肯定能统统忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 所以才特地跑到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这样的 因为我每年都会到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今年…想着「也告诉相川吧」什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.06,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步真是个幸福的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说那家伙是不是有点慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有熊出没很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:04.56,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女孩子独行是很危险的哟 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:09.48,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是内心脆弱的主人公相川步的脑补声音 CV:南央美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 春奈那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去看一下 大家在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说谢谢的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是特地带我到僻静的地方来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了 我才没…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激你 得回礼才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西就免了啦 不用感谢啊回礼什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因…因为我只是在做身为相川的妻子该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说相川 但是…如果无论如何都要回礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.16,0:11:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能叫…叫出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个？那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…那个…这个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能叫相川的名字…名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我叫咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步…步 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25}步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BBBB…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boys be ambitious
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心夜路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BBBB…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boys be ambitious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春奈 你居然依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀 步屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山里跟熊先生相会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要逃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见前面了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步 这绝非本意的情况 你应该有其相应的理由吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我说明一下 其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟步不一样可是深得动物厚爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样得意忘形小心被吃掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别嫉妒别嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在担心你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受欢迎男生的醋意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.83,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋伤脑筋（其实应该是こまった才对 くま是熊的意思 优也说冷笑话了）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:13:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直能跟相川在一起 好开心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那说法说得好像我们喜欢步一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很是火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们都跟着相川一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想跟友纪玩才到这来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.87,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在一起才开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 对不起 我太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家一起去看星星…才开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到山顶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人来爬这个难度太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的星星从以前开始就是那么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 不断演变的星星们也是如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很希望能让相川看到这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我得到勇气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都说了不用道谢了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友纪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年大家也一定要再一起来这啊 步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅尔·修特罗姆 你吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是煎蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给我这个煎蛋第一研究人&天才煎蛋厨师 春奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.31,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}三星级(三星级是餐厅的最高等级)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 可以叫你师父吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟过去那个懦弱的我道个别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 过去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 新的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川大人的签名 太想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后永别了 新的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的量 好厉害啊 相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 是大家太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请签名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情要持续到哪年哪月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那平静的日常究竟去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它泡在水里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.48,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你! 狗屎达令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份感情已经传达到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生 就像是经历着暴风雨的大海里被丢入的一艘小船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织户
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你之前为什么早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边可是出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 相川…同学是?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的是 现在的你对于我来说实在是过于遥远的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是当前的话题人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我所处的世界实在是相差甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说些什么啊 我就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然在全裸的前后 周围人变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 我的本质丝毫没有改变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.68,0:19:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 我对于自己的死党是个变态而且喜欢女装
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上他还成为了当今话题人物的这个现实 感到悲伤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还无法接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织户…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能 再给我点时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:20:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我这颗混乱的心…恢复平静为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 织户 我们永远都是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远什么的 果然不现实吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你的爱是永恒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提到能成为My darling的人 不就只有你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账垃圾达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听仔细了 你的魅力本小姐最清楚不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会亏待你的 尽管放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.75,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注目吧、对这美臀!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步臀祭 一口气就燃遍了天际啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.76,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变态「世界级」的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊啊啊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世人啊 尽情来体会My darling的魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该死心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你抓到会变成怎么样 我早就清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:22:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是想问你几个问题而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实回答的话 我是不会让你吃苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.17,0:23:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妄想优A
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:23:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是妄想优B
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.63,0:23:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人合起来并称双子优
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.99,0:24:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不需要这种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原版优
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.82,0:24:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 说白了你对于哥哥的魔装少女装是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见到的时候稍微有一点吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.09,0:24:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看惯了之后就上瘾了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.23,0:24:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能把那身行头穿的那么合身 真不愧是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.08,0:24:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能那么合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.63,0:24:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称赞过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.61,0:24:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.83,0:24:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次让他穿我们的服装吧 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.23,0:24:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 多谢收看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:39.76,ET,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,45)\fad(500,0)}「Yo! 那就是 基♂情!」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ByeBye~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.97,0:24:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ByeBye
